==Untitled== I believe that the Barracuda that ditched was from ''Indefatigable'' and that it ditched near its own carrier, not ''Formidable'', based on the account in McCart's history of the ''Illustrious''-class ships. The crew was recovered by the destroyer ''Verulam'', according to McCart, p. 150. You can find a full citation to the book on the {{sclass-|Implacable|aircraft carrier}} page.--[[User:Sturmvogel 66|Sturmvogel 66]] ([[User talk:Sturmvogel 66|talk]]) 01:27, 23 January 2014 (UTC) :Added, thanks a lot [[User:Nick-D|Nick-D]] ([[User talk:Nick-D|talk]]) 10:25, 26 January 2014 (UTC)
